INTRODUCTION
------------

Hi and welcome to nginZ.

NginZ is acronym of EngineZ. It's lightweight web site engine.

What's my idea? Simple engine for web sites with great look/design.

TECHNOLOGIES
------------

EngineZ is written in HTML5, CSS3 and PHP. Extensions of some files are .php, but most of code is HTML (under PHP).

GENERAL
-------

Project is released as open source software (OSS) under terms of PostgreSQL License (see LICENSE file). For more information about OSS see http://opensource.org/.

GET INVOLVED
------------

You can help me with forking this repo and testing.

* I will search all forks and see changes (commits). All fixes and pathes are welcome.
* Don't change master branch! That's stable branch. For your patches/fixes make new branch, like patch-1 or html-fix.
* For any suggestion and (beta/alpha) testing you can contact me on e-mail (see AUTHOR). You can also use Issues page for enhancements.
* Before submitting issue, search Google and see Wiki - https://github.com/ZDroid/nginZ/wiki. Also, search existing issues.

